Package: idaMakeDtm
Title: These functions create document term matrices in the format consistent
    with IDA's R-based text mining functions.
Version: 1.0
Authors: "Thomas W. Jones <twjones@ida.org>"
Maintainer: Thomas W. Jones <twjones@ida.org>
Description: These functions create document term matrices in the format
    consistent with IDA's R-based text mining functions. These functions are
    inputs to IDA's DTM-Making Shiny app.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1),
    tm,
    slam,
    Matrix,
    snowfall,
    RWeka,
    SnowballC
License: GPL
LazyData: true
